{"tid":1363801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月26機場集會","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T15:15:19.000Z","uid":8187,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef3812023feedbfabbfa50bc2c753565cb9b082","tid":1363801,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">日期：2019年7月26日（五）<br />\n地點：香港國際機場一號客運大樓－五樓接機大堂<br />\n時間：13:00 - 23:59</span><br />\n(不反對通知書申請中)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANFuA5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANFuA5h.jpg&h=889881e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scey2Lh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fscey2Lh.jpg&h=12b9faa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次機場集會係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">100%和理非行動</span></span><br />\n主要係要各外國旅官宣揚香港情況包括<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">- 5大訴求<br />\n- 黑警暴力 <br />\n- 官警黑勾結 <br />\n- 元朗恐怖襲擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為要向外國人講解6-7月發生既事<br />\n所以希望外語能力高既和理非巴絲<br />\n今次都入晒黎機場集會<br />\n多啲向外國人講解下我地既事情<br />\n同埋準備多啲英文傳單派比外國旅客<br />\n<br />\n其他人都希望你地可以入黎坐下<br />\n幫手派傳單<br />\n反正機場有冷氣又有靚靚空姐<br />\n成個6,7月既遊行集會都未試過咁舒服<br />\n咁難得有次係可以舒舒服服咁集會<br />\n就當係727光復元朗前入黎放鬆下<br />\n<br />\n最重要記住因為今次地點係機場<br />\n絕對一定要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和平理性非暴力</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b8c7ba1242f4af1cfb1d8cb01619ab6e03a1986","tid":1363801,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45528f9fa31831bd7f3c5a5907cb105586db041","tid":1363801,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}